data.description: Beautiful split level home in Mountain View! This property features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, one being off of the primary bedroom. There are good sized bedrooms, a kitchen island and a great covered back patio that looks out onto your fully fenced backyard! One car garage in basement as well as a large den/bonus room with a beautiful and large wood burning fireplace. Don't wait to see this great home in a great school district and no city taxes!
